name: Adnowspecsavers
title: Specsavers Ad Now
description: Understand the impact of your ad and how well it is building your brand

simple_settings.name: dtm_id
simple_settings.label: Marketplace Project ID
simple_settings.help_text: You can find this in the Project Request Confirmation email. If you do not have this, leave this field blank

simple_settings.name: linknow_database_fieldwork_country
simple_settings.label: Database fieldwork market
simple_settings.help_text: some markets have their database split by classifiers (region, city, language etc) and this field allows you to specify this

simple_settings.name: linknow_database_commissioning_country
simple_settings.label: Database commissioning market
simple_settings.help_text: This is the market that you are based in, NOT the fieldwork market

simple_settings.name: Engagement_module_required
simple_settings.label: Engagement section required?
simple_settings.help_text: This is the part of the survey that includes the questions for Enjoyment/Likeability, Active Involvement and Branding. PLEASE NOTE: You must select at least one of the Engagement, Predisposition and Association blocks at the study set up stage in order to launch a study.

simple_settings.name: Predisposition_module_required
simple_settings.label: Predisposition section required?
simple_settings.help_text: This is the part of the survey that includes the questions for Usage, Persuasion/Likelihood to Action, Difference and Affinity. PLEASE NOTE: You must select at least one of the Engagement, Predisposition and Association blocks at the study set up stage in order to launch a study.

simple_settings.name: Association_module_required
simple_settings.label: Association section required?
simple_settings.help_text: This is the part of the survey that includes the Message Check question. PLEASE NOTE: You must select at least one of the Engagement, Predisposition and Association blocks at the study set up stage in order to launch a study.
